data.description: Immaculate 3 bedroom, 2 bath split plan home located in DeBary Woods, one of DeBary's premier subdivisions.  Located at the end of the cul-de-sac, the only cars driving on this road belong to the residents that live on this road.  Home has a unique L-shaped garage and an oversized, park-like, shaded backyard with room for a pool!  Keep the grass green and the water bill low, this home comes equipped with an irrigation well!  As you step through the front door, the master bedroom is to your immediate  right and the other two bedrooms are split to your left.  Master bath features separate garden bath and shower stall, walk in closet, and his and hers sinks.  As you step past the foyer, the home opens up to a bright family room, kitchen combo with vaulted ceilings.  Family room is spacious with skylights providing substantial natural light.  Kitchen features a dinette with island and granite countertops.  French doors in the family room lead to a sizable, 17 by 11 screened back patio with wet bar.  Home features an indoor laundry utility room, tankless water heater, and natural gas!  This home is ideally located and in close proximity to restaurants, shopping, and healthcare facilities.  DeBary Woods is a great option for a buyer looking to avoid high HOA dues! It is 45 minutes to the attractions and 45 minutes to the beach. Minutes from historic Deland and Sanford downtown areas, Blue Spring State Park, Gemini Springs Park and the Sunrail station. Don???t miss out! Schedule your showing today!
